{"tid":1970692,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]Fifa 20 Pro club 球隊招經驗球員","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:02:41.000Z","uid":196359,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac84091023cdfdff3b82e38808f09987c8fe33d","tid":1970692,"uid":196359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"招經驗全位置球員打比賽<br />\n<br />\n1。招經驗全位置隊員，謝絕新手。各球員需有空間感、位置感及一定技術。有高超技術，不怕你英雄主義，但大家需溝通。<br />\n2。陣型隨機應變，按己方及對方球員制訂。<br />\n3。請提供主、副擅長位置，強項弱項。<br />\n4。防守需全隊配合、開咪提醒隊友。<br />\n5。進攻隊友互相配合，帶球、拉位、補位、不輕易失球，不會限死一套打法，盡量按隊友能力制定戰術。具體入隊再講<br />\n<br />\n球隊重組補強中, 望有能之士加盟長期夾波, 強隊需時間打磨。<br />\n<br />\n有意請add tg<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/GWfifa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGWfifa&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=90f21289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GWfifa</a>"},{"pid":"5d5ccde193799237aa16b4e06841a49802fcd80d","tid":1970692,"uid":196359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"298261a66747e0f2b195bc226640a8c52b2ccc59","tid":1970692,"uid":196359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a6a8426c6264d3817762c9ccfaaae133f520c80","tid":1970692,"uid":196359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有意tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/GWfifa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGWfifa&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=90f21289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GWfifa</a><br />\n或<br />\npsn: w02202000"},{"pid":"684dd5106515e338754394f9a72212c433b6c82d","tid":1970692,"uid":312758,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"咁多要求，<br />\n有無糧出？"},{"pid":"d03f12fb8428d1e1a9157526cea4122d5bc23e63","tid":1970692,"uid":196359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"